{"tid":989050,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone SE 在 Apple 官方商店重新上架促銷發售","createTime":"2019-01-20T14:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:06:29.000Z","uid":182854,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49a81e00c861f7a2b9c3141df61190eac10b651e","tid":989050,"uid":182854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"iPhone SE 非常長青，2016 年推出之後直到 2018 年才停止發售。不過最近 Apple 就在其官方商店的清貨促銷頁面重新發售 iPhone SE，把餘下的存貨清掉。<br />\n<br />\n據 MacRumors 發現，在美國的 Apple 網上商店，清貨促銷頁面上出現了 32GB 和 128GB 的 iPhone SE 供選購，價格分別是 249 美元和 449 美元，不過很快就已經賣完，在美國以外的 Apple 網上商店也沒有看到 iPhone SE 的出現。Apple 為什麼會重新出售 iPhone SE 仍然不清楚，但是在部分第三方商店則仍然有售 iPhone SE。<br />\n<br />\niPhone SE 是最後一款採用 4 吋螢幕的 iPhone，雖然之前一直傳聞 Apple 會推出 iPhone SE 2，不過過了幾年都仍然未有類似的產品出現，之前的 iPhone XR 被認爲是地位相近的產品，不過目前看來並沒有能夠吸引原先喜歡 4 吋螢幕的消費者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/iphone-se-unlocked-800x507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fiphone-se-unlocked-800x507.jpg&h=7ed4a70d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29d39565ae003a6b969996ef5ede6eca6a3784ca","tid":989050,"uid":209225,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T22:52:34.000Z","msg":"之前的 iPhone XR 被認爲是地位相近的產品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff8d9665245c355a3f317a248caff55611099a4","tid":989050,"uid":37136,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"29d39565ae003a6b969996ef5ede6eca6a3784ca","tid":989050,"uid":209225,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T22:52:34.000Z","msg":"之前的 iPhone XR 被認爲是地位相近的產品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cl